        "text": "Attacks by Task forces 8 and 17 wore successfully carried out today except that heavy rain decreased the effectiveness of that against Jaluit. He sul ts : By T.P. 17 Llakin - 1 auxiliary badly damaged, two seaplanes destroyed. Jaluit - 1 out of two auxiliaries badly damaged;1 no aircraft present. Mill - Nothing present. (Seven of our airdraft lost).",
