        "text": "Task Forces Eight and Seventeen continued their retirement . Task Force Eight approaching Task ^orce Eleven. The number of patrol planes at Johnston Island was increased to six to assist in covering these forces. Later, Vice Admiral Halsey reported that his force had sufficient fuel to reach Pearl.",
