        "text": "No indication of the operations of Task Forces 11 and 17 plus Anzac Force was received until about 1600 when a contact report was made by the eneny Gunboat Division EIGHT in the Rabaul area. Also no report of the results of the raid by the B-17s on the northeast coast of Hew Guinea (Comanzac 091300) was received.",
        "degraded": false
