        "text": "No change in operations of task forces today. A letter giving the proposed task organization of the Fleet wa3 sent to COMINCH via Capt. Duncan. By this, the Scouting Force and Battle Force are done away with. Vice Admiral Brown will command the Amphibious *'orce; Vice Admiral Pye the Covering Force (3B'3 and accompany ships of other types).",
