        "text": "The Pacific Ocean Area was quiet except for submarine contacts at Christmas. i ^ Small allied bombing raids by air were made on Lae, ^ Vunakanau, Lukunai, Rabaul, and Paisi. These raids undoubtedly cause the enemy demage and slow down his offense.",
