    "command": "ADM. C. W. NIMITZ, CINCPAC",
    "actual": [
      {
        "text": "Opnav (221724) is going to ship material such as A/T protection, mooring bvoys , etc., to Auckland, Suva, Nandl and Noumea. The general defense and supply for our advanced oases will undoubtedly improve when Admiral Ghormley takes charge. Captain Bowman took over at Auckland today. CIncpac (250357) makes some of the old Anzac surface force and 12 VP available to Task Force 17. The general S.W. Pacific situation remains the same.",
        "degraded": true
      }
    ],
