        "text": "Com. Gen. ROSES 191759 recommends occupation of ESPIRITU SANTO. This is concurred in by prospective ComSftttPac. The CO. also desires at least two more infantry regiments. The desire for more troops seems general as C.G. STRAW also wants more. The logistic item mu3t be considered before all men requested are sent. Comairsopac (191120) wants more civilian personnel . CinCPac 200113 urges COMINCH action at STRATOOARD. See aidac in this connection which directs action to be taken.",
