      {
        "text": "( -S*t •'e* w bo &<ra\\ The French occupied WALLIS 26th local. A It is estimated that BLEACHER will be ready in all respects £une 21st. Task Force 16 entered Pearl. Admiral Halsey has some kind of skin trouble and was sent to the hospital.",
        "degraded": true
      }
