        "text": "The consolidation of positions In the TULAGI area continues with Fletcher's striking forces standing by to prevent Jap reinforcements. A comparati vely large number of enemy cruisers, destroyers, transports, and freighters have been sighted recently in the RABAUL area. This constitutes a threat to our Marines, but also offers a fine target for Fletcher if they ever cone within his reach. A force of 1 CL 2 DD and 4 AKs was thought heading toward GUADALCANAL. Attack planes took off, but as the force turned away, no contact was made. The BLUE was ordered scuttled as she could not be towed.",
